public enum Settings
extends java.lang.Enum<Settings>
implements ValueByEnum.JungleJeppsEnum

This file represents an ENUM for every setting needed for Jungle Jepps Desktop configuration. This is used to as the key in a key-value persistence storage system in the SettingsManager.

Author:
Joel Jeske
